      "body_lines": [
        "COLOMBO (News 1st); A 46-year-old resident of the Kirulapana area personal has died after falling from a 12-storied building in Wellawatta.",
        "Sri Lanka Police said that the deceased was engaged in cleaning activities on the 11th floor of the building."
